Constructors

constructor

  • new Plane(anchor: VectorOrList, v1: VectorOrList, v2?: VectorOrList): Plane
    • Defined in src/plane.ts:23

    Creates a plan from the anchor point and normal to the plane. If three arguments are specified, the normal is calculated by assuming the three points should lie in the same plane. If only two are sepcified, the second is taken to be the normal. Normal vector is normalised before storage.

    Parameters

    • anchor: VectorOrList
    • v1: VectorOrList
    • Optional v2: VectorOrList

    Returns Plane
